sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Zammad (Customer)
    participant BE as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant AI as CrewAI Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant T as Telegram
    participant O as Dashboard (Operator)

    C->>BE: Webhook / Polling (Tiket Baru)
    BE->>DB: Simpan ke tabel Ticket & AuditLog
    BE->>C: Auto-reply "Halo, laporan diterima..."
    BE->>AI: Trigger Analisis AI (Tier 0)
    AI->>AI: Eksekusi Llama-3 & Cari Solusi
    AI-->>BE: Kirim Hasil Diagnosis & Solusi
    BE->>C: Update Tiket Zammad dengan Solusi AI
    BE->>T: Notifikasi Tiket Baru ke Telegram IT
    BE->>O: Update Dashboard via WebSocket
